-- News Express: Sony's Shakeup
-- B y
-- 2012-03-22T04:18:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-22/news-express-sony-s-shakeup.html
Sony falls at the start of Tokyo 
trading from reports that incoming CEO Kazuo Hirai plans a 
leadership shakeup by naming studio Chairman Michael Lynton as 
CEO of U.S. entertainment. Emirates Airline says more carriers 
will go bust this year on rising fuel costs and sluggish 
economies.  Goldman Sachs Group Inc. (GS)  indicates it's a good time 
to buy into equities. Bloomberg's Susan Li reports. (Source: 
Bloomberg)  Running Time: 02:48
 